                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Opon what brittle<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Piers - </l>
                    <l>Our Faith doth<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 daily tread - </l>
                    <l>No Bridge below<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 doth totter so </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="Yet">and</add>
Yet - none hath such<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 a Crowd - </l>
                    <l>It is as old as<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 God -</l>
                    <l>Indeed - 'twas built<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 by him - </l>
                    <l>He sent his son<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to test the Plank </l>
                    <l>And he pronounced<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 it firm - </l>
